dc_title_s: A new map of America from the latest observations
dc_creator_sm: Senex, John, -1740."Harris, John, fl. ca.1685-ca. 1720 engraver.
dc_description_s: Revis'd by I. Senex. |Relief shown pictorially. Dedication in title cartouche to [Henry Bowes Howard,] Earl of Berkshire, deputy earl marshal of England. Shows California as an island. Includes elaborate decorative cartouche in the upper left corner. The cartouche depicts scenes of Native American life, such as battle and food as well. 1 map: outline col.; 47 x 55 cm.
